Class TEXTLibrary

  com.intexsoft.cli.model.AbstractLibrary

All Implemented Interfaces:
Library
public class TEXTLibrary
extends AbstractLibrary

Implementation the abstract class AbstractLibrary.
Class for work with TEXT-libraries. In TEXT-library information about books witch stores in files:
01.properties, 02.properties, ...
In each file can store information abount only one a book.
Example:

 Index=1000
 Author=Asimov
 Name=Foundation
 Issued=2006.12.10
 Issuedto=Yavorchuk
